  "notes": [
    "This study represents the first comparative genomic analysis of hepatocellular carcinoma between chimpanzees and humans",
    "The high frequency of TSC2 mutations in chimpanzee HCC (80% vs 7% in humans) suggests species-specific oncogenic pathways",
    "Chimpanzee HCC samples showed significantly higher mutation burden than human samples, even after controlling for technical artifacts",
    "The study used both whole genome sequencing (1 pair) and whole exome sequencing (4 pairs) from chimpanzee samples"
  ]
